  <brief_title>Fibrinogen in Haemorrhage of Delivery</brief_title>
  <acronym>FIDEL</acronym>
  <official_title>Study on the Efficacy and Safety of a Therapeutic Strategy of PPH Comparing Early Administration of Human Fibrinogen vs Placebo in Patients Treated With IV Prostaglandins Following Vaginal Delivery</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
